OL,5, An armed officer who fatally shot a man
OL,6, during a police stop on a motorway slip
OL,7, road has told an inquest the suspect   
OL,8, pointed a gun at him before he fired.  
OL,10,FYassar Yaqub, 28, was the front-seat   
OL,11,Fpassenger in one of two cars travelling
OL,12,Fin convoy on the M62 when four covert  
OL,13,Fpolice cars surrounded them in 2017.   
OL,15,FThe inquest at Leeds Crown Court       
OL,16,Fpreviously heard an officer fired three
OL,17,Fshots at Mr Yaqub from 5ft (1.5m) away.
OL,19,FTwo of the bullets hit him in the chest
OL,20,Fand caused "catastrophic blood loss".  
